Supporting both Ethereum and Solana? Or maybe Cosmos and Avalanche? Maintaining multiple versions of your app for different chains is a nightmare.

With Shogun, you only need to deploy once, and it automatically works across multiple blockchains.

Imagine a scenario where users come to your app with assets from various chains—Ethereum, Solana, BSC, and more. 

With Shogun, no matter what assets your users hold, they can interact with your app effortlessly.
